Interface NondetModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Model
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    CTMDP, LTS, MDP, MDPGeneric<Value>, NondetModelSimple, STPG
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CTMDPSimple, LTSExplicit, LTSFromDA, MDPAdditionalChoices, MDPDroppedAllChoices, MDPDroppedChoicesCached, MDPEquiv, MDPExplicit, MDPFromDTMC, MDPSimple, MDPSparse, MDPView, ParamModel, STPGAbstrSimple, STPGExplicit, SubNondetModel

    public interface NondetModel
extends Model
    Interface for (abstract) classes that provide (read-only) access to an explicit-state model with nondeterminism.
